This project allows to run an api mockup with  [json-server](https://github.com/typicode/json-server).

##Start the API
1. install json server globally `npm install -g json-server`
2. run the server and specify the port `json-server --watch db.json --port 3001`  <br/>
if you want to change the port don't forget to change the port in the client under '//config'

Check db.js to get an idea over the data structure or visit :
*documentation
http://localhost:3001

##API endpoints
* get all currencies<br/>
http://localhost:3001//currencies
* get all currencyConversions<br/>
http://localhost:3001/currencyConversions
* get time currency conversion
http://localhost:3001/timeCurrency

Please check documentation for more



